Set Up Queue-Based Routing for Calls:

Create queue and routing configuration prior to setting up call routing.
From Setup, enter Voice and select Amazon Contact Centers or Partner Telephony Contact Centers.
Add phone channel and edit its routing settings.
Route calls to a specific Salesforce queue by selecting "Queue" in Call Routing Type field.
